theorem exists_ball_eq_zero_of_deriv_apply {U : Set â„‚} (hU : IsOpen U) {f : â„‚ â†’ â„‚} (hf : AnalyticOn â„‚ f U)
    {zâ‚€ : â„‚} (hzâ‚€ : zâ‚€ âˆˆ U) (h_eq : Â¬ âˆ€ z âˆˆ U, f z = f zâ‚€) (h_deriv : deriv f zâ‚€ = 0) :
